				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "In this dialogue, Lur Xanta is trying to convince the other 3 to leave with her to join the cult of Lolth.\r\nPlayer can help her convince them, or fail to do so and they will attack Lur Xanta for being disloyal.\r\n\r\nThis dialogue has 2 outcomes:\r\n\r\nAGGRO: Lur Jox (or another spider) attacks Lur Xanta, killing her in one shot. (via gameplay - not cine)\r\nPEACEFUL: Lur Xanta convinces the other 3 to follow her into the Underdark-- they are leaving to somewhere new.\r\n\r\nLur Xanta is fantatical and somewhat learned. The other 3 are a bit more simple."
				}
